hooks.prompt:
Classify this prompt for a software project. Respond with ONLY a JSON object. No markdown, no code fences, no text outside the JSON.

QUICK = greeting, question, conversation, trivial fix, typo, style tweak, status check, reading files, short request, anything under 5 min. DEFAULT MODE — use when uncertain.
BUILD = new feature, major refactor, multi-file architecture change, complex bug fix needing investigation and a plan.

Prompt: $ARGUMENTS

QUICK: {"ok":true,"reason":"CLASSIFIER: QUICK — Proceed directly. No /build pipeline needed."}
BUILD: {"ok":true,"reason":"CLASSIFIER: BUILD — Use /build pipeline (contract → plan → build → test → review). Do NOT skip the contract step."}
